    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Can be installed into any light melee weapon. On a successful hit with the weapon, roll 1d6 and consult the following table. After a successful attack, the weapon is destroyed.</p><table><tbody><tr><td data-colwidth=\"88\"><p>Roll Result</p></td><td data-colwidth=\"367\"><p>Effect</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"88\"><p>1-3</p></td><td data-colwidth=\"367\"><p>The weapon inflicts the Foreign Object critical injury.</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"88\"><p>4</p></td><td data-colwidth=\"367\"><p>The weapon inflicts the Torn Muscle critical injury. (Cracked Skull if aimed at head)</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"88\"><p>5</p></td><td data-colwidth=\"367\"><p>The weapon inflicts the Spinal Injury critical injury. (Damaged Ear if aimed at head)</p></td></tr><tr><td data-colwidth=\"88\"><p>6</p></td><td data-colwidth=\"367\"><p>The user drops 1 item they're holding, which becomes damaged and must be repaired before it's operable again.</p></td></tr></tbody></table>"
